<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>{{ webapp_site_title }}</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; margin: 4rem auto; max-width: 40rem; color: #1a1a1a; }
      h1 { color: #0b6; }
      code { background: #f0f0f0; padding: .1rem .3rem; border-radius: .2rem; }
      .meta { color: #555; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>{{ webapp_site_title }}</h1>
    <p>Diese Seite wurde automatisiert per <strong>Ansible</strong> und
       <strong>Docker Compose</strong> bereitgestellt.</p>
    <p class="meta">Host: <code>{{ inventory_hostname }}</code>
       &middot; IP: <code>{{ ansible_host }}</code></p>
  </body>
</html>
